1.title: Second Skin
1.plot: Many experts believe aliens have visited the Earth for thousands of years, but if we can't survive space travel without a protective suit, how can they? Are some aliens mere shells or clones with an artificial consciousness?

2.title: The 1952 Wave
2.plot: In the spring of 1952, UFO sightings go off the charts. For years, the U.S. government has told the postwar public that UFOs do not exist, but behind the scenes, U.S. Air Force officials are divided.

3.title: The Freedom of Information Act
3.plot: In 1969, the U.S. government officially announces it will stop investigating UFOs, but declassified documents reveal that multiple government agencies have been hiding important UFO sightings for decades.

4.title: The Space Force
4.plot: Since the early 1960s, we've experimented with how to travel off planet Earth. Many experts believe America has operated a secret Space Force for decades, with ultra high-tech ships designed for missions beyond Earth's orbit.

5.title: The Shoot Down Order
5.plot: Since the Jet Age, fighter pilots have been scrambled to intercept UFOs in our skies, but what happens when pilots are sent a Shoot Down Order and can't complete their mission?

6.title: Seeing Is Believing
6.plot: For decades, governments around the world have investigated UFO sightings, often times under an umbrella of secrecy. How are these top-secret studies conducted? Who is called upon to analyze the evidence?

7.title: Inside UFOs
7.plot: Alien abductions are the only types of encounters in which eyewitness testimony can reveal details about the inside of UFOs. Details that can help us understand how aliens live and what they want from the human race.

8.title: Unwelcome Visitors
8.plot: If aliens have visited Earth, why are they here and what are they truly after? Investigations have revealed the possibility that aliens are interested in experimenting on not only the human body, but the human mind as well.

9.title: Alien Journeys
9.plot: In order to survive mankind must find a way to navigate the galaxy. Alien encounters have offered a possible glimpse into the secrets of interstellar flight, but how would extraterrestrials know how to navigate the vast regions of space?

10.title: Finding Aliens
10.plot: Rapid advancements in science and technology have given mankind unprecedented access to distant galaxies that could harbor life. And some scientists believe that to find alien life we need look no further than our own backyard.

11.title: UFO Photos
11.plot: Photographic evidence of Unidentified Flying Objects helped usher in the modern UFO phenomenon. As the world continues to evolve into the digital age, more and more people are capturing images in the sky that they are unable to explain.

12.title: UFOs from Earth
12.plot: Where do UFOs come from? Some people believe they're from distant galaxies, wormholes, or other planets within the Milky Way. Join us as we investigate the existence of UFOs and determine the possibility that they may be from Earth.

13.title: Summer of Saucers
13.plot: In 1947, a series of UFO sightings triggers an unprecedented analysis that propels the UFO phenomenon on to the world stage. We investigate how the U.S. Air Force comes to the stunning conclusion that UFOs may not be from Earth.

14.title: Police Sightings
14.plot: UFO sightings happen almost every day. But in the court of public opinion the most credible witnesses come from law enforcement. Join us as we investigate the most important police sightings of UFOs.

15.title: Space Shuttle Encounters
15.plot: Between 1981 and 2011, NASA's Space Shuttles flew 135 missions. The Space Shuttle cameras, manned and unmanned, have recorded astounding footage of UFOs that many experts find almost impossible to explain.

16.title: Mass Sightings
16.plot: Many famous UFO sightings occur in remote locations with just a single eyewitness. But some sightings have taken place over large cities with hundreds of witnesses.

17.title: Mars, the Final Frontier
17.plot: Scientists have never been closer to proving that life once lived on Mars. But is it still there? And if so, how has it evolved? Join us as we investigate the red planet and the possibility that alien life may live within our own galaxy.

18.title: Alien Communications
18.plot: Scientists and Ufologists are scouring the vast regions of space for signs of extraterrestrial life. But if it takes millions of years for light from distant stars to reach Earth, how long could it take for aliens to answer our call?

19.title: Artificial Alien Intelligence
19.plot: Some scientists believe the survival of mankind hinges upon the revolutionary science of Artificial Intelligence. Biological life may just be an evolutionary stepping-stone in a universe dominated by Artificial Alien Intelligence.

20.title: First Contact
20.plot: For decades, scientists have been searching for proof that extraterrestrials exist. But just where does alien life exist? And what does it look like? Join us as we investigate just how close we are to First Contact.

1.title: Alien Encyclopedia
1.plot: The Blue Planet Project, a book that allegedly is an exhaustive account of extraterrestrial activity on Earth, is discussed.

2.title: Cracking the Alien Code
2.plot: A tale is told of a 1980's sighting by U.S. servicemen of an landed unknown craft in Britain's Rendlesham Forest from which one of the servicemen received telepathically a message in binary code after touching the craft.

3.title: UFO Portal L.A.
3.plot: Using significant selected sighting events before 1900 to present, a case is made that Los Angeles experiences abnormally numerous UFO incidents.

4.title: Aliens and the Vatican
4.plot: Details from art works, miraculous visions and Vatican investigations and archives are used to support a theory that the Roman Catholic Church has concealed its knowledge of extraterrestrial life.

5.title: Aliens on the Moon
5.plot: Tampered space photos, missing NASA recordings and a race to the moon all point to one very likely possibility: alien life exists, and our universe is anything but our own.

6.title: Alien Plagues
6.plot: Throughout history, unexplained illnesses have repeatedly attacked the human population with a vengeance.

7.title: Secret Alien Tech
7.plot: We live in the golden age of technology. But is everything around us a testament to the power of the human brain or did we have help? And if aliens did have a hand in our technological advancement, what did we give up in exchange?

8.title: Top 10 Alien Plots
8.plot: Ten tales of aliens, UFOs and abductions, a fresh look at classic encounters and several new stories

9.title: Alien Implants
9.plot: We have always been told that mankind enjoys free will. Is this really true? Or have aliens created the means for controlling humanity? The shocking truth might just be hidden inside you.

10.title: Nazis and UFOs
10.plot: Adolf Hitler set out to conquer the world and he nearly succeeded. But did the Nazis have help from an extraterrestrial source? We'll tell you what Hitler may have been hiding - and where it is now.

11.title: Aliens Among Us
11.plot: They live and work in your town. In fact, they may be members of your country's government. But they're not who, or what, they appear to be. We'll unseal the truth about these aliens among us.

12.title: Solway Firth Spaceman
12.plot: The connection to mysterious men in black, the failure of missile tests in 1964 and a series of same year photographs of a man's daughter in which one of the frames mysteriously appears a man in a spacesuit is examined.

13.title: Aliens and Presidents
13.plot: Anecdotal reports of encounters of Presidents of the United States with alien crafts and races are chronicled.

14.title: Alien Gods of Egypt
14.plot: Selected papyrus writings, hieroglyphic carvings and architectural achievements are presented as possible proof that ancient Egyptians interacted with or were even ruled by extraterrestrials.

15.title: Top 10 Alien Plots
15.plot: After a review of conspiracy theories concerning extraterrestrial visitors, various ufologists speculate about aliens' possible good or bad motives.

16.title: Life on Mars
16.plot: Findings of NASA Mars missions are used to explore whether intelligent life exists or has existed on the planet and whether this life might be source of such life on Earth.

17.title: Men in Black
17.plot: Theories about the origins and identity of the menacing, eerie men of near identical appearance dressed in identical black dress who visit persons with UFO involvement are presented.

18.title: Aliens and the Military
18.plot: The list of global threats to the human race is long. But could Earth's armed forces be facing a new enemy that is out of this world? We expose military evidence that governments have long been preparing for the next great global conflict.

19.title: Roswell and Area 51
19.plot: Arguments that favor a 1947 air crash at Roswell, New Mexico did involve extraterrestrials as supported by activities at the mysterious Nevada military facility known as Area 51 are discussed.

20.title: Forbidden Places
20.plot: UFO phenomena occur all over the world, from remote places to the skies over the world's major cities. But if aliens are among us then where are they hiding? Are governments harboring extraterrestrial life in remote and forbidden places?

21.title: British X-Files
21.plot: Former British MOD official Nick Pope comments on selected incidents extracted from the release of fifty years of declassified British UFO reports for which Pope had significant oversight.

22.title: Alien Hot Spots
22.plot: Incidents of unusual sightings in Los Angeles, Texas, the United Kingdom and China where these type of sightings are statistically higher are recounted.

1.title: Majestic 12
1.plot: An extraterrestrial threat. A top secret organization. Has the US made contact with aliens? Experts believe they have. And an ultra top secret organization is calling all the shots. Get ready for the untold story of Majestic 12.

2.title: The Kecksburg Incident
2.plot: Many UFO sightings are solitary events that leave witnesses scrambling to prove their story. But what happens when the same object is seen by many people at the same time? Join us as we expose the hidden secrets of The Kecksburg Incident.

3.title: Unidentified Submerged Objects
3.plot: More than half the world's UFO sightings happen over water. Many of these phenomena are seen bursting from the ocean into the sky. Do aliens lurk in our oceans? Join us as we expose the growing threat of Unidentified Submerged Objects.

4.title: The Laredo Incident
4.plot: What does the American government really know about UFO's? And how far will they go to hide the truth? In 1948 a fireball crashes near Laredo, Texas. They say it was an experimental aircraft. But many experts believe it was a UFO.

5.title: Soviet UFOs
5.plot: The Soviet Union's vast skies paid witness to thousands of UFO sightings. But the Soviet regime was notorious for secrecy. Many of their encounters reported during the Cold War had potentially deadly consequences for the entire world.

6.title: Fatal Encounters
6.plot: Encountering life from another world can be a terrifying and deadly experience. Abductees claim to have been captured and experimented on. Join us as we confront the truth about alien encounters.

7.title: Aliens and Civilization
7.plot: There are structures as old as time that continue to baffle historians and engineers the world over. Did we build these ancient megaliths ourselves or did aliens guide our hand?

8.title: Alien Plunder
8.plot: Everyday, UFOs are spotted in skies all over the world. But of all the planets in the known galaxy, why have they come to Earth? Are aliens here to seize Earth's riches? And how far does their mission go?

9.title: Bedroom Invaders
9.plot: Close encounters. There's no telling where or when they will happen. But of all the possible scenarios, none is more terrifying than the one we're unaware of - until it's too late.

10.title: Alien Messages
10.plot: Signals from deep space. Mysterious crop circles. Messages hidden in the very building blocks of our planet. Recent evidence may reveal signs of alien life attempting to communicate. Are they goodwill ambassadors, or masters of war?

11.title: Blackouts!
11.plot: Recently, the US has experienced massive blackouts effecting millions of people and throwing their lives into sudden chaos. Do these blackouts occur as a side effect of alien technology? Or is there a darker agenda at work?

12.title: Alien Earth
12.plot: Our world is changing. Temperatures are climbing. Ocean levels are rising. Giant storms are becoming more frequent and intense. Super-viruses are thriving in this new environment. At the same time, alien activity is also on the rise.

13.title: Earth Federation
13.plot: Humanity has been plagued by international conflicts and epic powers since the dawn of time. Perhaps our greatest failure is constant strife and division. Could an alien threat force humans to form a united front?

14.title: The World Grid
14.plot: Pyramids are found all over the world and from different time periods in human history. Did humans build the pyramids by themselves - or did they have help? Some experts believe pyramids across the world are part of a grand alien design.

15.title: UFO Crash Retrieval
15.plot: For decades, eyewitnesses have reported UFOs crashing to Earth all over the nation. Most are never found. Some believe crashed UFOs may contain alien technology that could change the course of history.

16.title: The Watchmen
16.plot: For decades, citizen UFOlogists have coordinated alien information-sharing networks, subverting the classified intelligence of their governments. What do these classified documents say about the way that our governments watch the skies?

17.title: The Sun
17.plot: The sun. It's an immense powerhouse on a scale that almost defies the imagination. And it's the source of all life here on Earth. But what if that power was being tampered with? Are UFOs really visiting our Sun?

18.title: Alien Spaceships
18.plot: Each year, there are thousands of UFO sightings all over the world. What are these different kind of UFOs? What is each craft's purpose? What powers them and how they are controlled? And most importantly- who is flying them?

19.title: UFOs Down Under
19.plot: Aborigines have the oldest continuous culture on Earth. Rock paintings and ancient legends suggest that aliens have been communicating with Australian Aborigines for 70,000 years. What are the Sky Being's relationship with these people?

20.title: Controlled Panic
20.plot: For over sixty years authorities the world over have been inundated with highly credible reports of UFOs. But according to experts, many governments have gone to great lengths to cover-up the truth about extraterrestrial life.

1.title: Alien Origins
1.plot: What are UFOs? Are they spacecraft? Do they travel vast distances to reach planet Earth? From mysterious planets at the edge of the Solar System, to epic journeys beyond the boundaries of time and space.

2.title: Human Harvest
2.plot: Nearly three hundred million people worldwide claim to have been abducted by aliens. Many report being subjected to torturous medical experiments. Others return with unwelcome reminders of their ordeal. Are aliens creating human hybrids?

3.title: Astronaut Encounters
3.plot: In the 1960s we too our first steps into a vast new realm-bound for the Moon. But NASA astronauts would soon find they weren't the only ones out there.

4.title: Atmospheric Anomalies
4.plot: Some experts believe many atmospheric light shows are actually caused by extraterrestrials. Do they pose an imminent threat to humanity? Join us as the alien secrets behind atmospheric anomalies.

5.title: Alien Apocalypse
5.plot: Millions of people believe extraterrestrial live on Earth. Are the aliens here to enlighten us or destroy us? What if the worst-case scenario happened? What would aliens do? And how would they do it?

6.title: Top 10: Military Encounters
6.plot: They're our first line of defense in the darkest of times. And they're often the first responders to threats from another world. Over the past 70 years the world's military forces have come face to face with thousands of UFOs.

7.title: Alien Skies
7.plot: Every day, millions take to the sky in commercial flights all over the world. But decades of evidence have revealed we may not be the world's only frequent flyers. Are we in danger of losing control of our skies to extraterrestrial beings?

8.title: The Next Wave
8.plot: It's the stuff of nightmares. Emergency lines flooded with calls as UFOs appear in the sky. Mounting evidence has revealed that UFO waves are able to penetrate the world's most closely guarded airspace.

9.title: Signs of Abduction
9.plot: It's the ultimate close encounter. There have been thousands of reported cases all over the world. But these claims are almost invariably dismissed by authorities with little or no investigation.

10.title: Antigravity
10.plot: UFOs. They can fly at blinding speed. Or hover effortlessly just a few feet above the ground. And they can do it all without making a sound. But how is this possible? The mysteries of anti-gravity propulsion are unsealed.

11.title: UFO Metals
11.plot: Nations all over the world are rumored to have recovered metal debris from these UFO crashes. From self-healing hulls to sinister alien implants, join is as the secrets of UFO metals are UNSEALED.

12.title: Triangle Terror
12.plot: The flying saucer. For decades it's been synonymous with UFO terror. But millions of reported encounters tell a very different story. From Cold War showdowns to telepathic terrors, join is as we track the rise of Black Triangles.

13.title: Earth Portals
13.plot: Experts have long believed the universe to be riddled with mysterious portals - shortcuts through space that allow travelers to span vast distances in the blink of an eye. From mighty volcanoes to secret underground civilizations.

14.title: Solar System UFOs
14.plot: Do visitors to planet Earth come from some far off galaxy? Traveling vast distances to the only planet boasting intelligent life in this corner of space. We investigate the shocking secrets of alien civilizations in our solar system.

15.title: Nazi UFOs
15.plot: The Nazis. Led by Adolf Hitler, they were the greatest evil the world has ever known. In just ten years, Hitler took Germany from crushing depression to world domination. Did the Nazis have access to alien technology?

16.title: Alien Bodies
16.plot: Do aliens exist? And have they visited planet Earth? These are perhaps the most important questions of our time. For decades, eyewitnesses have come forward with unsettling stories of alien bodies recovered from crashed UFOs.

17.title: UFO Zones
17.plot: Our world is home to many UFO hot spots, where unidentified objects are reported with alarming regularity. But a select few locations have something extra. They're notorious for strange paranormal phenomenon to extraterrestrial activity.

18.title: Countdown to Disclosure
18.plot: For decades, UFO researchers have demanded that the government reveals what is knows about UFOs. Who will make the announcement? When will they do it? And what will it mean for the very bedrock institutions of society?

19.title: Top Ten Civilian Encounters
19.plot: It can happen to anyone at anytime; a close encounter with a UFO. Citizens all over the world have been reporting incidents with alarming increase. We are counting down the top ten civilian close encounters of all time.

20.title: Alien Achilles Heel
20.plot: Many believe aliens are already here on Earth. But why are they here? Are aliens planning an all-out attack on planet Earth? And if they are, is there any way we can fight back?

imdb.title: Unsealed: Alien Files
plot: Unsealed Alien Files investigates documents of alien and UFO encounters, made accessible to the public by the Freedom of Information Act. Each episode tackles a compelling alien case by opening these previously off-limit secret files.
